Changes:
 ros-one-vision-msgs (0.0.2-2024.10.19.11.55) sid; urgency=high
 .
   * Added BoundingBox2DArray message #60 <https://github.com/ros-perception/vision_msgs/issues/60> from Fruchtzwerg94/array_for_2d_bounding_box
